1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 22=

4
00:01:12,079 --> 00:01:15,159
Yiqing, tell me everything
that happened on the way here,

5
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:17,439
from beginning to end.

6
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:18,200
Alright.

7
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,120
At first,

8
00:01:19,239 --> 00:01:20,439
everything seemed normal.

9
00:01:20,700 --> 00:01:22,480
But after we reached
the foot of Mount Nanhua,

10
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,670
I overheard the guards
talking inside the carriage.

11
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:25,000
They said...

12
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:28,120
The master from the palace
usually acts like a living bodhisattva,

13
00:01:28,310 --> 00:01:29,799
but turns out she's just as ruthless.

14
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,660
Now that they've arrived
at Mount Nanhua,

15
00:01:31,670 --> 00:01:32,670
there's no way
they'll make it out alive.

16
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,040
Hey.

17
00:01:33,050 --> 00:01:33,920
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

18
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:34,599
Shut your mouth.

19
00:01:38,239 --> 00:01:40,159
Then why didn't you tell
His Majesty just now?

20
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:42,799
I was afraid he might be
that so called bodhisattva.

21
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:44,519
It couldn't be him.

22
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:45,940
How does he
look anything like a bodhisattva?

23
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:46,760
Then who else

24
00:01:46,879 --> 00:01:48,200
in the palace could be called one?

25
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,680
Could it be...

26
00:01:50,799 --> 00:01:51,760
Dowager Consort Liu?

27
00:01:52,359 --> 00:01:54,680
She was the first to go to Mount Nanhua,

28
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:57,359
and the Liu family
has always wanted more power.

29
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,040
It's not impossible.

30
00:01:59,159 --> 00:02:00,359
Grandfather

31
00:02:00,359 --> 00:02:01,760
is still missing.

32
00:02:01,879 --> 00:02:03,480
What if something happens to him?

33
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:04,840
Don't worry.

34
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:05,879
We'll find him.

35
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:08,919
This...

36
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,199
These prayer beads...

37
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,400
Weren't they buried years ago?

38
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,960
Back then, Grandfather said

39
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,520
these beads were unlucky.

40
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,840
What kind of prayer beads

41
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,479
have one hundred and nine beads?

42
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:20,039
Take them off right now.

43
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:22,280
One hundred and nine?

44
00:02:32,159 --> 00:02:33,400
You're right.

45
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:35,639
How could this happen?

46
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:37,879
Yiqing,

47
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,159
do you still remember

48
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:41,199
the person
who used to meet with my mother?

49
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:42,560
Why bring him up?

50
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,520
After Aunt was drowned,

51
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:46,080
he never appeared again.

52
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:48,319
He was from the same hometown
as your mother.

53
00:02:48,639 --> 00:02:49,919
What a heartless man.

54
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,759
He was from the same hometown
as my mother?

55
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:53,520
Yes.

56
00:02:53,879 --> 00:02:54,639
I heard

57
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:56,280
they even grew up together.

58
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,000
Then can you be sure

59
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,240
it was really a man?

60
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,520
Of course it was a man.

61
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,520
I just don't know his name.

62
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,560
Grandfather never allowed
anyone to mention him.

63
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,800
That man even secretly

64
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:12,159
came to see Aunt twice.

65
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,919
Grandfather was furious over it.

66
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:15,879
I really don't know

67
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,240
what spell Aunt was under.

68
00:03:17,250 --> 00:03:18,750
Not only did she insist on seeing him,

69
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:21,479
she even followed him
to Mount Nanhua to gather herbs.

70
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,800
(Could it really be as I suspected?)

71
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:28,159
(Could Madam Lian
have disguised herself as a man?)

72
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,000
This is bad.

73
00:03:29,039 --> 00:03:30,080
Bao'er is missing.

74
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:30,759
What?

75
00:03:31,310 --> 00:03:32,319
That little troublemaker.

76
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:33,670
How could she run around like this?

77
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,970
What if she gets taken away
by that so called bodhisattva?

78
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,400
It's alright. Don't worry.

79
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:38,840
Stay here. I'll go look for her.

80
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,759
An assassin has entered the palace.

81
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:44,479
Every corner must be searched carefully.

82
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,319
No place can be overlooked.

83
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,080
Yes.

84
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,439
Whose child is this?

85
00:03:57,039 --> 00:03:58,439
I'm from Lady Shen's side.

86
00:03:58,439 --> 00:03:59,120
What?

87
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:02,439
Shen Zhinian
actually has a child this old?

88
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:05,120
His Majesty even brought
her child into the palace?

89
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:06,560
Are you a consort too?

90
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:07,479
You're so pretty.

91
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,919
What's the point of being pretty?

92
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,010
His Majesty still likes

93
00:04:11,020 --> 00:04:12,759
your mother,
who's not even pretty at all.

94
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:14,599
My mother is pretty too.

95
00:04:14,599 --> 00:04:16,600
My mother will hit you with a pot lid.

96
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:19,040
You're not allowed
to talk about my mother like that.

97
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:21,240
Don't cry.

98
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,079
Hey, don't cry.

99
00:04:23,439 --> 00:04:24,199
No crying.

100
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,839
Your Majesty,

101
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,439
you even brought
her child into the palace.

102
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:30,040
Do you love her that much?

103
00:04:30,110 --> 00:04:31,580
What nonsense are you talking about?

104
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,439
Bao'er.

105
00:04:33,759 --> 00:04:34,439
Bao'er.

106
00:04:34,759 --> 00:04:35,279
Bao'er.

107
00:04:35,519 --> 00:04:36,220
Come here quickly.

108
00:04:36,519 --> 00:04:37,240
Don't cry anymore.

109
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,519
It's alright now.

110
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:39,639
Your Majesty,

111
00:04:39,879 --> 00:04:40,920
please don't scare Bao'er.

112
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,560
Your Highness.

113
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:42,759
When did I scare him?

114
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,600
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

115
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,480
I shouldn't have offended you.

116
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,600
Shen Zhinian,

117
00:04:51,759 --> 00:04:52,519
my chest hurts.

118
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:01,040
Your Majesty, stop acting like a child.

119
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,600
You're not hurting at all.

120
00:05:04,399 --> 00:05:05,199
Shen Zhinian,

121
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,120
even if you gave me
just a little of your affection,

122
00:05:08,519 --> 00:05:09,399
I'd still be happy.

123
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:14,120
It's not that I don't like you.

124
00:05:17,010 --> 00:05:17,879
I just don't dare to.

125
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,439
Why?

126
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:23,639
Actually,

127
00:05:26,199 --> 00:05:27,639
both Shen Nanqiao and I

128
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,519
were given a second chance at life.

129
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:33,270
In the previous life, she entered
the palace and became your consort.

130
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,560
But not long after,

131
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,079
you sentenced her to death.

132
00:05:36,879 --> 00:05:38,600
The Shen family
and my grandfather's family

133
00:05:38,750 --> 00:05:40,600
were both accused
of colluding with the enemy.

134
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,560
That day,

135
00:05:43,079 --> 00:05:45,000
the streets of Chizhou
ran red with blood.

136
00:05:45,900 --> 00:05:47,980
Before Bao'er died,
she was still crying out to me.

137
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:50,839
Auntie, save me.

138
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:54,340
♪Flowers wither easily,
but obsession remains♪

139
00:05:54,340 --> 00:05:57,700
♪The world is gentle only because of you♪

140
00:05:58,879 --> 00:05:59,879
Impossible.

141
00:06:01,110 --> 00:06:03,580
I saw with my own eyes
how my mother and Madam Lian suffered.

142
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:06,079
That's why I never
harm women or children.

143
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:11,480
Before I knew you,

144
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:13,079
I thought

145
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:16,040
you were cruel,

146
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:17,800
violent, and unpredictable.

147
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,079
But after getting to know you,

148
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:22,220
I realized there must
be hidden reasons behind everything.

149
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,560
Even so, I still don't dare to love you.

150
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:27,759
I'm afraid that one day,

151
00:06:28,060 --> 00:06:29,519
my whole clan will be executed again.

152
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,839
That's why

153
00:06:32,279 --> 00:06:33,720
I kept trying every way possible

154
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,890
to get the death-exemption medal
and the blank imperial decree from you.

155
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,759
All I wanted was to keep my family safe.

156
00:06:39,380 --> 00:06:42,420
♪Love etched into my bones
is beyond concealment♪

157
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:45,540
♪Even in the deep palace filled
with sorrow and longing♪

158
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:47,680
I don't understand
this so called previous life,

159
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:49,600
but I understand myself.

160
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:52,079
I would never hurt you.

161
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:55,100
♪I walk through the palace
day and night, just for my beloved♪

162
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:58,340
♪All my tenderness is for you,
I'd stay alone for you♪

163
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:00,800
Auntie,

164
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:02,600
is His Majesty my uncle in law?

165
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,600
No.

166
00:07:03,879 --> 00:07:05,759
His Majesty is the Son of Heaven.

167
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,120
He's the Emperor.

168
00:07:07,199 --> 00:07:09,680
Then why is he holding your hand?

169
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,839
Only an uncle in law

170
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,959
can hold Auntie's hand.

171
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:14,990
I'm your uncle in law.

172
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,040
Come on.

173
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:18,600
I will take you
to find your great grandfather.

174
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,180
After dropping Bao'er off,

175
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:24,759
I want to go see Shen Nanqiao.

176
00:07:26,060 --> 00:07:27,920
They've already
searched this place thoroughly.

177
00:07:28,199 --> 00:07:29,319
If there was anything here,

178
00:07:29,350 --> 00:07:30,839
it should've already been taken away.

179
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,959
But Shen Nanqiao has a habit.

180
00:07:33,439 --> 00:07:35,560
She writes down anything
she can't remember.

181
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:39,720
Since she deliberately wanted
to help Lu Jianglin rise to power,

182
00:07:39,730 --> 00:07:41,790
she definitely would've
used knowledge from her previous life

183
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:43,920
to help him earn merit
and advance his career.

184
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:03,920
I knew she'd hide it away
so Lu Jianglin wouldn't find out.

185
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:07,560
That way, she could feed him
information piece by piece,

186
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,480
and he'd have no choice
but to follow her lead.

187
00:08:12,060 --> 00:08:13,680
(At the Thousand Autumn Banquet,
Jiang Wanning is named Consort)

188
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:16,839
At the Thousand Autumn Banquet,
Jiang Wanning is named Consort.

189
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,800
So in the previous life,
there really was a Consort Jiang.

190
00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:24,079
Looks like she became
your second Empress.

191
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,600
Impossible.

192
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,480
She must've made it up.

193
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:35,600
Empress Jiang recovers from her illness
and resumes control of the harem.

194
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,039
She recovered?

195
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,000
Well, that's good.

196
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,600
If she truly recovers,

197
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:43,160
then I can at least give Jiang Chen
some peace of mind.

198
00:08:48,039 --> 00:08:49,600
You and Jiang Chen fell out?

199
00:08:51,100 --> 00:08:54,000
(After the Thousand Autumn Banquet,
Nangong Xuanyu executes Jiang Chen.)

200
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:54,639
Your Majesty.

201
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:57,960
Your Majesty.

202
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,110
The Prince of Jin has been found.

203
00:08:59,120 --> 00:08:59,919
Where is he?

204
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:01,000
He escaped the city.

205
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,879
Find him at all costs.

206
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:12,399
I've completed everything
master ordered.

207
00:09:12,679 --> 00:09:14,320
When will master let me live again?

208
00:09:14,519 --> 00:09:15,519
Don't rush.

209
00:09:15,879 --> 00:09:17,120
What's meant to be yours

210
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,720
won't be missing a single piece.

211
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,120
There's one more thing

212
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,720
I need you to do.

213
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,279
Yes.

214
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,879
Write another vertical stroke.

215
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:31,759
Hey.

216
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:35,720
Young Lady, Lady Liu wants
to see you for questioning.

217
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:38,240
Later, have someone
keep an eye on Bao'er.

218
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,519
Don't let him run off.

219
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,370
Practice properly on your own.

220
00:09:41,399 --> 00:09:43,799
Today, you must get this
horizontal stroke right.

221
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:44,960
I will check when I come back.

222
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:45,559
Okay.

223
00:10:16,639 --> 00:10:17,279
Lady Liu.

224
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:18,720
Lady Liu.

225
00:10:18,879 --> 00:10:20,000
Shen Zhinian?

226
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,320
Why are you here?

227
00:10:21,759 --> 00:10:22,799
Who dares tie me up?

228
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:23,720
Which fool did this?

229
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:25,279
I'll have his head cut off.

230
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,399
Keep your voice down.

231
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:29,679
Who did you offend this time?

232
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:31,480
You even dragged me into this.

233
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:33,519
In this palace,

234
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,639
who would dare kidnap even you?

235
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,240
Could it be Dowager Consort Liu?

236
00:10:37,559 --> 00:10:38,440
Nonsense.

237
00:10:38,610 --> 00:10:40,000
That old woman Liu
is still counting on me

238
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,590
to help her fight
for the position of second Empress.

239
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,519
She'd never kidnap me.

240
00:10:44,190 --> 00:10:45,399
Then could it be the Empress?

241
00:10:46,310 --> 00:10:47,559
That doesn't make sense either.

242
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:49,720
She may be fake and vicious,

243
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,120
but she's half dead already.

244
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:52,399
Why would she kidnap us?

245
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:53,840
The Empress...

246
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:55,879
Is she really sick?

247
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,240
Isn't she?

248
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,879
She's coughing up blood all day.

249
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:01,240
Now every time she opens her mouth,

250
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:03,060
I feel like she's about
to spray blood at me.

251
00:11:10,399 --> 00:11:10,919
Hey.

252
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,399
Let me go right now.

253
00:11:12,399 --> 00:11:13,800
And I'll spare your worthless life.

254
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,879
You dare kick me?

255
00:11:17,279 --> 00:11:18,519
Lu Jianglin, stop!

256
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:19,080
What?

257
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,039
Lu Jianglin?

258
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,320
He's not dead?

259
00:11:32,679 --> 00:11:33,440
Come with me.

260
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,960
Shen Zhinian,

261
00:11:54,519 --> 00:11:56,440
things weren't supposed
to turn out this way.

262
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:59,559
The one you were supposed
to marry was me.

263
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,480
I'm sorry.

264
00:12:03,039 --> 00:12:04,000
I was wrong.

265
00:12:04,759 --> 00:12:06,759
I never should've married Shen Nanqiao.

266
00:12:08,159 --> 00:12:09,799
But I just couldn't accept it.

267
00:12:10,399 --> 00:12:12,399
Why did you abandon me?

268
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:15,480
I wanted to make something of myself,

269
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,480
make you regret leaving me.

270
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:19,759
Let go of me.

271
00:12:22,679 --> 00:12:23,320
I'm sorry.

272
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:24,440
I'm sorry.

273
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,600
Listen to me.

274
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,440
Once I finish helping them,

275
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,679
I'll negotiate with them.

276
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,399
I don't want anything anymore.

277
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:34,240
I just want to take you back to Chizhou.

278
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:37,519
From now on, we'll never step foot
in the capital again.

279
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,919
We'll live a good life together, alright?

280
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,799
Who are you helping?

281
00:12:50,039 --> 00:12:50,919
Lady Liu.

282
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,000
Nonsense.

283
00:12:54,010 --> 00:12:56,190
I've already been kidnapped by you,
and now you're trying to frame me too?

284
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:58,320
Those eunuchs were too stupid.

285
00:12:58,639 --> 00:13:00,559
I never expected them to kidnap her too.

286
00:13:01,330 --> 00:13:03,799
Someone secretly reported
that those eunuchs were using this place

287
00:13:03,799 --> 00:13:05,480
to smuggle palace valuables out.

288
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:07,919
Stop right there.

289
00:13:11,159 --> 00:13:13,200
So someone
really is up to shady business.

290
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:14,600
Renran,

291
00:13:14,879 --> 00:13:15,840
open the barrels.

292
00:13:16,159 --> 00:13:18,159
I want to see what they're hiding.

293
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:18,919
Yes.

294
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,120
Shen Zhinian?

295
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:29,390
You actually dared to smuggle consorts
out of the palace to sell for money?

296
00:13:29,519 --> 00:13:30,879
You two are dead.

297
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,120
Earlier,

298
00:13:34,559 --> 00:13:36,080
she humiliated me like that.

299
00:13:36,639 --> 00:13:38,159
We might as well kill her too.

300
00:13:39,399 --> 00:13:40,039
Then...

301
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,480
Then we can run away together.

302
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:45,960
Lu Jianglin, you're such an idiot.

303
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,840
You're even more foolish
than Shen Nanqiao.

304
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:48,759
Enough!

305
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,399
Shen Zhinian,

306
00:13:50,399 --> 00:13:52,919
I've had enough
of your self righteous attitude.

307
00:13:53,020 --> 00:13:54,759
Other than writing poetry
better than me,

308
00:13:54,759 --> 00:13:55,990
what exactly makes you superior?

309
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,320
I'm better than you in every way.

310
00:13:57,799 --> 00:13:59,120
If I were truly born a man,

311
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:00,480
I'd stand higher than you,

312
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,440
fly farther than you,

313
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:02,639
and I definitely wouldn't end up

314
00:14:02,639 --> 00:14:03,960
like a stray dog the way you have.

315
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:04,919
You vile woman.

316
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:06,300
I've been far too lenient with you!

317
00:14:16,279 --> 00:14:16,919
Your Highness,

318
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:19,080
Lu Jianglin kidnapped Lady Liu as well.

319
00:14:20,159 --> 00:14:21,720
How dare he act on his own?

320
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:22,900
Renran escaped and came back.

321
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:24,990
She said that while she
and Lady Liu were inspecting the area,

322
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,720
they discovered eunuchs
had kidnapped Shen Zhinian

323
00:14:26,730 --> 00:14:28,490
and planned to smuggle her
out of the palace to sell.

324
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:30,840
Like master,

325
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:32,120
like servant.

326
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:34,990
How could they even imagine
someone was trafficking palace consorts?

327
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:38,010
Since they've already been captured,

328
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:39,720
have Lu Jianglin deal with them too.

329
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,240
Don't spare Lu Jianglin either.

330
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,360
Haven't I warned you again and again

331
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:53,480
to clean things up properly?

332
00:14:56,679 --> 00:14:58,519
Leave Shen Zhinian to me.

333
00:14:58,879 --> 00:15:01,360
You've visited my Fengqi Palace
more in the past half month

334
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:02,799
than you did all year before.

335
00:15:03,450 --> 00:15:05,159
Don't tell me
you've really fallen for her.

336
00:15:05,290 --> 00:15:06,279
Don't try to act clever.

337
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:08,000
You're the one fooling yourself.

338
00:15:08,250 --> 00:15:10,470
Do you really think
His Majesty sees you as a brother?

339
00:15:14,260 --> 00:15:15,919
Every time you get close to Shen Zhinian,

340
00:15:16,039 --> 00:15:16,919
he knows about it.

341
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:19,200
He's always been someone

342
00:15:19,330 --> 00:15:21,120
who clearly separates
gratitude from grudges.

343
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:23,990
The only reason he's lived
peacefully with us all these years

344
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:26,000
is because he remembers

345
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:28,240
how we protected him
when we were children.

346
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,720
You make a good point.

347
00:15:35,039 --> 00:15:36,500
But things have already come to this.

348
00:15:36,799 --> 00:15:37,879
If you and I still want

349
00:15:37,879 --> 00:15:39,840
to live peacefully
with His Majesty in the future,

350
00:15:41,519 --> 00:15:42,919
then one person must be sacrificed.

351
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:59,440
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

352
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:06,400
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

353
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:10,400
♪If we don't meet♪

354
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:13,840
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

355
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:20,560
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

356
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:27,360
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

357
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:34,040
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

358
00:16:34,560 --> 00:16:41,240
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

359
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:48,120
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

360
00:16:48,360 --> 00:16:54,240
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

361
00:16:55,160 --> 00:17:01,760
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

362
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:08,600
♪Wanting to fold my heart
into a paper kite♪

363
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:15,320
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

